<section class="product-trust-stack">
  <div class="product-trust-stack__inner page-width">
    <div class="product-trust-stack__intro">
      <p>{{ section.settings.eyebrow }}</p>
      <h2>{{ section.settings.title }}</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="product-trust-stack__grid">
      <article>
        <span>01</span>
        <h3>Will it actually last?</h3>
        <p>Dense Himalayan cheese texture gives dogs a longer supervised chewing job than soft treats or quick snacks.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <span>02</span>
        <h3>Is the size right?</h3>
        <p>The chew estimator matches by breed, weight, age, and chewing style so customers are not guessing at checkout.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <span>03</span>
        <h3>Is it safer than rawhide?</h3>
        <p>Prime yak chews are rawhide-free and made with simple ingredients. Always supervise and remove small end pieces.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <span>04</span>
        <h3>What happens at the nub?</h3>
        <p>When the chew gets small, remove it and puff it in the microwave after soaking to create a crunchy second treat.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .product-trust-stack {
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #24130d;
    padding: clamp(46px, 6vw, 78px) 0;
  }

  .product-trust-stack__inner {
    display: grid;
    gap: 28px;
  }

  .product-trust-stack__intro p {
    color: #d2632e;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 850;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .product-trust-stack__intro h2 {
    font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 48px);
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 780px;
  }

  .product-trust-stack__grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 14px;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
  }

  .product-trust-stack__grid article {
    background: #f6f1e9;
    border: 1px solid #eadfce;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 22px;
  }

  .product-trust-stack__grid span {
    color: #d2632e;
    display: inline-block;
    font-weight: 900;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .product-trust-stack__grid h3 {
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.12;
    margin: 0 0 10px;
  }

  .product-trust-stack__grid p {
    color: #6f5a50;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 989px) {
    .product-trust-stack__grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .product-trust-stack__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Product trust stack",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "eyebrow",
      "label": "Eyebrow",
      "default": "Buying confidence"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "title",
      "label": "Title",
      "default": "The questions every dog parent asks before buying"
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Product trust stack"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
